snippet.title: It's NOT OK at all! It's UTTER GARBAGE! DISAPPOINTING Diner!!!
snippet.description:
American Roadside Diners, Burgers, Pancakes, Waffles, Homes Fries, Philly Cheesesteaks, Hot Dogs, Shakes, the list goes on as the menu is huge. The American Diner made famous on Hollywood movies. Anyone who visits The United States always puts a visit on their list of things to do, and those who live in the USA it's an American Tradition. 

The OK Diner say that they provide an authentic diner experience from the rock and roll to the stacked burgers, griddle favourites, bottomless coffee plus wings and dogs (that’s chicken wings and hot dogs to you). All served up in a classic diner setting with a smile. 

The BIG Question is, can the UK replicate an American Diner right here in England?

Check them out for yourself...
https://okdiners.com
